name: Super Saffira & Little Hell:P Taking Over The World

metadata.description:
The Taking Over The World collection gives you full access to the Super Saffira Discord and ensures you are recognized as an early supporter of the Super Saffira project.
Holding these NFTs will give you access to lots of original content, special gifts, and early access to all future collections.

Thank you for being part of our family.

Welcome To Freedom.
